==Filipino==
===Pronunciation===
*ee-loh-kah'-noh

===Noun===
'''Ilokano'''
#a language spoken in the [[Philippines]], particularly in the northern provinces of [[Luzon]], in the Ilocos and Cagayan Region, it has very strong Spanish influences. Phrases from Spanish is  embedded and used in the language. 
#speakers of the Ilokano language

===Adjective===
'''Ilokano'''
#Pertaining to the people who speak the Ilokano language. People originating from Ilocos.

